Role-Based Risk Identification
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Understand role-based risk assessment in organizational security contexts
Identify security risks associated with different organizational roles
Develop a Python tool for analyzing role-based security risks
Apply Cyber Threat Intelligence (CTI) data to risk calculations
Generate risk reports and classify roles by risk level
Prerequisites
Basic Python programming knowledge
Understanding of JSON file formats
Familiarity with Linux command line
Basic knowledge of organizational security concepts
